 ☐ Syntax Confusing
   1. xxx：yyy vs ：xxx => yyy
   <%= form_tag(add_to_cart_product_path, :method => "post") do %> 
   <%= form_tag(add_to_cart_product_path, method: "post") do %> 

   2. xxx： ：yyy
   <%= select_tag(:num, options_for_select(select_num_arr, selected: :num)) %>

   3. w/wo ()
   <%= form_tag(add_to_cart_product_path, :method => "post") do %> 
   has_many :cart_items, :dependent => :destroy

   4. "" vs ''(what is the convention?)
   <%= form_tag(add_to_cart_product_path, :method => "post") do %> 
   <%= form_tag(add_to_cart_product_path, :method => 'post') do %> 
 
